title: Opie & Jim Norton JUN 01 2015 Mon.mp3
description:
THANKS TO @SternGeek for the file.

Today on Opie and Jimmy, we the start the show recapping the weekend and discussing Bob Kelly's party yesterday, we talk about the crane accident in NYC, we discuss helping people, and John Kerry breaks his leg.

We talk about Revenge Porn, Silk Road, and the deep web. Comedian Godfrey joins the show, we watch Tracy Morgan on the Today Show, and Jason Statham stops by.

We discuss action movies, and we watch video of a soccer team having an orgy in Thailand
